{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"7655b","heading":"Forestry products advanced utilization research","label":"7655b Forestry products advanced utilization research","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch103/schIII/ptB","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsA prior , title VI, , , which was not classified to the Code, was repealed by , , .section 617 of Pub. L. 105–185112 Stat. 607Pub. L. 107–171, title VII, § 7302116 Stat. 455June 23, 1998May 13, 2002","Amendments2018—Subsec. (f)(1). substituted “2023” for “2018”.Pub. L. 115–334"],"amendments":["Prior ProvisionsA prior , title VI, , , which was not classified to the Code, was repealed by , , .section 617 of Pub. L. 105–185112 Stat. 607Pub. L. 107–171, title VII, § 7302116 Stat. 455June 23, 1998May 13, 2002","Amendments2018—Subsec. (f)(1). substituted “2023” for “2018”.Pub. L. 115–334"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Establishment","label":"a Establishment","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall establish a forestry and forestry products research and extension initiative to develop and disseminate science-based tools that address the needs of the forestry sector and their respective regions, forest and timberland owners and managers, and forestry products engineering, manufacturing, and related interests.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Activities","label":"b Activities","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"wood quality improvement with respect to lumber strength and grade yield;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the development of novel engineered lumber products and renewable energy from wood; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F1%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"enhancing the longevity, sustainability, and profitability of timberland through sound management and utilization.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Demonstration activities and technology transfer to demonstrate the beneficial characteristics of wood as a green building material, including investments in life cycle assessment for wood products.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"forestry products, lumber, and evaluation standards and valuation techniques;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"lumber quality and value-based, on-forest management techniques; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fb%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"forestry products conversion and manufacturing efficiency, productivity, and profitability over the long term (including forestry product marketing).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Grants","label":"c Grants","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall make competitive grants to carry out the activities described in subsection (b).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Priorities","label":"2 Priorities","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"are multistate, multiinstitutional, or multidisciplinary;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"have explicit mechanisms to communicate results to producers, forestry industry stakeholders, policymakers, and the public; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2%2FC%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"extensive history and demonstrated experience in forestry and forestry products research;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2%2FC%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"existing capacity in forestry products research and dissemination; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/2/C","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F2%2FC%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a demonstrated means of evaluating and responding to the needs of the related commercial sector.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"Administration","label":"3 Administration","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In making grants under this section, the Secretary shall follow the requirements of paragraphs (4), (7), (8), and (11)(B) of subsection (b) of .section 3157 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Term","label":"4 Term","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term of a grant made under this section may not exceed 10 years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Coordination","label":"d Coordination","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall ensure that any activities carried out under this section are carried out in coordination with the Forest Service, including the Forest Products Laboratory, and other appropriate agencies of the Department.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Report","label":"e Report","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the research that has been conducted under paragraph (2) of subsection (b);","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the number of buildings the Forest Service has built with wood as the primary structural material; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Fe%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the investments made by the Forest Service in green building and wood promotion.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Authorization of appropriations","label":"f Authorization of appropriations","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/f/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Ff%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this section $7,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2014 through 2023.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Matching funds","label":"2 Matching funds","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/f/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7655b/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7655b%2Ff%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"To the extent practicable, the Secretary shall match any funds made available under paragraph (1) with funds made available under .section 1646 of title 16","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
